episodes.title: Is Dr. Berg really a narcissist, child abuser and cult member? w/ Ian Rafalko
EP17  IAN RAFALKO
episodes.description:
Ian escaped the cult of Scientology and sheds light on his famous father, @Drberg 

Heartbreaking and illuminating. Pulling back the veil on Scientology and going deep on what actually happens in this secretive "church".
